{"tid":2052933,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"卿姐為咩要咁做？ 齊阿哥:有人想破壞新一輪BNO居英計劃","createTime":"2020-06-06T01:30:03.000Z","updateTime":"2020-06-06T07:11:14.000Z","uid":30561,"like":9,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"995a28d70375ee3df1c301c4d9a33dd5ef91e004","tid":2052933,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T01:30:04.000Z","msg":"卿姐為咩要咁做？ 齊阿哥:有人想破壞新一輪BNO居英計劃<br />\n匪共出盡方法高調反對英國俾香港人走，<br />\n對香港人黎講係危險警號，因為匪共想要香港d錢。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IldpFV9ak48&amp;list=PLVir5JZoVIktERNBVHlxDRob07xJlRCq-&amp;index=676&amp;t=0s\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.youtube.com%2Fwatch%3Fv%3DIldpFV9ak48%26list%3DPLVir5JZoVIktERNBVHlxDRob07xJlRCq-%26index%3D676%26t%3D0s&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=b700a870\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=IldpFV9ak48&amp;list=PLVir5JZoVIktERNBVHlxDRob07xJlRCq-&amp;index=676&amp;t=0s</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/bODBgsR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FbODBgsR.jpg&h=f2a783c1&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">可以話英國做得唔夠.<br />\n但咁屌法, 可以幫到件事咩?<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/posts/828833304311808\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fgoodbyehkhellouk%2Fposts%2F828833304311808&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=d2654b1d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/goodbyehkhellouk/posts/828833304311808</a><br />\n<br />\nGoodbye HK, Hello UK</span></span><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/e0od22V.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2Fe0od22V.png&h=6267e67e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Zvwy228.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZvwy228.png&h=285af80d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/Rdmjd9W.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FRdmjd9W.png&h=21f78838&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n28分鐘 &middot;<br />\n<br />\n【好文共賞】<br />\n<br />\n卿姐好嘢！真係代表咗一類香港人！<br />\n（無話邊個，總之對返個位入座，唔該！）<br />\n<br />\n香港女民主吉祥物之一嘅卿姐，今日去信《The Times》編輯部，數臭英國政府同首相Boris Johnson，仲比編輯推到頂置，可以話係幫一類人出咗一口污氣呀....<br />\n<br />\n「比二百幾萬個BNO留低只係小恩小惠，香港人仍然係覺得被（英國人）出賣囉。」<br />\n<br />\n「响1984年，戴卓爾夫人簽中英聯合聲明嗰時，我親自問佢，將五百萬香港人交比共產統治，道義上講唔講得通？」<br />\n<br />\n「三十六年之後，真正嘅恐懼終於出現喇，唯一嘅方法係英國比所有香港人擁有居留權，一點也不能少，少一個都係可恥同信唔過！」<br />\n<br />\nP.S. 响呢個Page見唔少嘅言論，估唔到响《The Times》出現，好驚喜呀喂！感動到想喊！洗唔洗揾問米婆，叫戴卓爾夫人上黎回應下？<br />\n<br />\n#最強召喚<br />\n<br />\n傳送門：<br />\n《The Times》<br />\nLETTERS TO THE EDITOR<br />\nJohnson&rsquo;s offer of refuge for Hongkongers<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/comment/times-letters-johnsons-offer-of-refuge-for-hongkongers-h7z5srcz7?fbclid=IwAR112qvED5SQZmbqM8o7N-F6WKDdwCkPcGCXm0B-3CN4Zc4xTyDWBSFFRpE\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thetimes.co.uk%2Fedition%2Fcomment%2Ftimes-letters-johnsons-offer-of-refuge-for-hongkongers-h7z5srcz7%3Ffbclid%3DIwAR112qvED5SQZmbqM8o7N-F6WKDdwCkPcGCXm0B-3CN4Zc4xTyDWBSFFRpE&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=de555713\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.thetimes.co.uk/edition/comment/times-letters-johnsons-offer-of-refuge-for-hongkongers-h7z5srcz7?fbclid=IwAR112qvED5SQZmbqM8o7N-F6WKDdwCkPcGCXm0B-3CN4Zc4xTyDWBSFFRpE</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">另外認可反對派開始在關鍵時刻做嘢：</span><br />\n<br />\n黎智英接受CNBC訪問：美國不應取消香港特殊待遇<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.cnbc.com/2020/06/04/the-us-should-not-revoke-hong-kongs-special-status-jimmy-lai.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.cnbc.com%2F2020%2F06%2F04%2Fthe-us-should-not-revoke-hong-kongs-special-status-jimmy-lai.html&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=a4b03590\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.cnbc.com/2020/06/04/the-us-should-not-revoke-hong-kongs-special-status-jimmy-lai.html</a><br />\n香港人日日retweet有用咩，大台一句勁過你日日 retweet 一萬次。<br />\n為民主犧牲嘅成千上萬嘅香港人如何？難道係#大鳴大放#嘅運動？<br />\n<br />\n公民黨：希望保持香港獨立關稅區地位<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073960\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073960&d=hYhEKVoQeS8%2B2u2S5aPGGab0OKgTvMyjK8k7SjVk7cc%3D&h=d382c7d7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.inmediahk.net%2Fnode%2F1073960&h=77b497d2\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.inmediahk.net/node/1073960</a><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4vhFJaY.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4vhFJaY.jpg&h=659fff17&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n等 「認可反對派」贏左35+坐低慢慢同匪共傾？ 匪共好驚35+？<br />\n比你哋傾咗23年，重唔夠？"},{"pid":"eba5ba6652f65ba6493e21849f78674b696200a1","tid":2052933,"uid":30561,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T01:36:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jRE49UU.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjRE49UU.png&h=9e89c359&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"6377f1b8fac85a9f1c6700b739cb7f086248bae7","tid":2052933,"uid":94968,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T01:37:11.000Z","msg":"飯民"},{"pid":"4e14137ac97624b86c168687279dccfca00ceca2","tid":2052933,"uid":30561,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T01:38:25.000Z","msg":"今次BNO條件已經很好，難得脫左歐，須要好多工人，英國找份工唔難，不過唔會太高，又唔一定專業人，反低工仲好，娤修，清潔，收銀等等，一定無人爭。"},{"pid":"d3b1b7c7e5f67ef0bbb912df6c0461e9f039036d","tid":2052933,"uid":253978,"like":0,"dislike":15,"score":-15,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T01:38:59.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"7f81a7070245afb194315311b10f47ab4e983f1a","tid":2052933,"uid":351663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-06-06T01:39:27.000Z","msg":"垃圾飯民"},{"pid":"f2176b84353d0ad07c3c3ac11f716adb48cdf41d","tid":2052933,"uid":30561,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"quote"